{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "e44d5c12-349f-4321-ba81-123456789abc",
        "name": "Plantsitter API",
        "description": "# Plantsitter API Documentation\n\nWelcome to the Plantsitter Backend API! This collection contains all the necessary endpoints to interact with the system.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n1. **Environment**: Ensure the `base_url` variable is set to your server address (e.g., `http://<ELASTIC_IP>:8000`).\n2. **Authentication**: Most endpoints require authentication. \n    - Use the `Auth / Login` request first.\n    - The collection is configured to **automatically** save the `access_token` from the login response to your environment variables.\n    - All other requests automatically use `Bearer {{access_token}}` for authorization.\n\n## Structure\n\n- **Auth**: User registration, login, and profile management.\n- **Plants**: Core plant analysis, detection, and collection management.\n- **Weather**: City-based weather alerts and plant care tips.\n- **Achievements**: Gamification system stats and unlocking logic.",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Auth",
            "description": "Endpoints for user authentication and profile management.",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Register",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"securepassword123\",\n    \"name\": \"New Gardener\"\n}",
                            "options": {
                                "raw": {
                                    "language": "json"
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "auth",
                                "register"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Start here! Creates a new user account. \n\n**Note**: Returns an access token so you can start using the app immediately."
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
                {
                    "name": "Login",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "// Automatically save the token for future requests",
                                    "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "if (jsonData.access_token) {",
                                    "    pm.environment.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access_token);",
                                    "    console.log(\"Login Successful: Access Token updated automatically.\");",
                                    "}"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
                            "options": {
                                "raw": {
                                    "language": "json"
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "auth",
                                "login"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Authenticates a user and returns a JWT token.\n\n**Automation**: This request contains a visualizer script that automatically extracts the `access_token` from the response and saves it to your Environment variables. You do NOT need to copy-paste the token manually."
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
                {
                    "name": "Get Profile",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}",
                                "type": "text"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/me",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "auth",
                                "me"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Returns the currently logged-in user's profile details."
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
                {
                    "name": "Update Profile",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "PATCH",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}",
                                "type": "text"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"city\": \"Mumbai\",\n    \"balcony_orientation\": \"North-East\"\n}",
                            "options": {
                                "raw": {
                                    "language": "json"
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/me",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "auth",
                                "me"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Updates profile fields. Useful for setting the 'City' to enable weather alerts."
                    },
                    "response": []
                }
            ]
        },
